<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0;">        tx:</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;"> 95.781</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;"> kB/s</span></span>
